the popular resistance forces launched a major attack against a 
commando unit inside the al-'Amarah marshlands. The regime's 
troops were forced to retreat, leaving behind many dead troops 
and several destroyed vehicles. The regime's artillery pounded 
areas in [word indistinct], killing a civilian and injuring four 
others. 

