BFN 

  [Excerpt] Russian President Boris Yeltsin's special envoy, 
who is visiting Kuwait, stressed the importance of Iraq's 
compliance with international resolutions pertinent to Kuwait's 
liberation war. 
  This statement was made during a meeting between envoy 
Yevgeniy Shaposhnikov and Shaykh Sabah al-Ahmad Al Sabah, first 
deputy prime minister and minister of foreign affairs, held at 
