  [Text] Major General Ilan Biran, commander of Central 
Command, today decided to impose a closure on Jericho to allow 
the heads of the Palestinian police in the city to organize. 
The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] wishes to make sure that all 
the Palestinian policemen stationed in the city are clear on 
their authorities and powers pertaining to Israeli citizens 
traveling inside Jericho. The decision came in the wake of a 
series of incidents over the past few days, including this 
morning's incident. 

</TEXT>

