Hatim Hamdan al-'Azzawi, chief of the Presidential Office; 
ministers; those who hold the rank of minister; and fighter 
members of the General Command of the Armed Forces. 
  President Saddam Husayn thanked the well-wishers, wishing 
everyone, and through them the children of our great Iraqi 
people and the glorious Arab nation, continued glory and a 
prosperous future, God willing. 

</TEXT>

