<F P=100> Iran </F>
<H3> <TI>   Daily Reports 700 Killed in Hajj Stampede </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Daily Reports 700 Killed in Hajj Stampede </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2405111694 Paris AFP in English 1108 GMT 24 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2405111694 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tehran, May 25 (AFP)--A stampede at the pilgrimage 
in Mecca killed 700 people on Monday [24 May], the daily KAYHAN 
[as received] reported on Tuesday quoting its correspondent in 
the Saudi city. Quoting "unofficial sources" in Saudi Arabia, 
it said six of the dead were Iranians. 
  A Turkish official has spoken of 182 dead while other eye 
witnesses put the total at more than 200. 

</TEXT>

