BFN 

  [Text] Khartoum, 25 May (MENA) -- Sudanese security 
authorities tonight seized the residential quarters of the 
Egyptian Community School teachers along with the administrative 
headquarters of the Egyptian education mission in Khartoum. The 
Sudanese authorities expelled the teachers from their quarters 
and assembled them in one location. 
