<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Our correspondent Karmela Menashe reports that 
following a decision by Major General Ilan Biran, the commander 
of the Central Command, from 1700 [1400 GMT] Palestinian traffic 
will once again be permitted to enter and leave Jericho. In the 
meantime, Israeli traffic will be permitted only along Route 90, 
which cuts through Jericho, and no diversions will be allowed. 

