  [Text] Brother Shaykh 'Abdallah Bin-Husayn al-Ahmar, 
[Yemeni] House of Representatives speaker, arrived in Abu Dhabi 
last night heading a delegation on a two-day visit to the 
sisterly United Arab Emirates [UAE]. 
