  [Text] Brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, 
Presidential Council chairman, today met with leaders of 
political parties and organizations; unions; professional 
associations; and popular, creative, and professional 
organizations; and with shaykhs, ulemas, and representatives of 
the youth, women, and all national forces and figures in the 
entire Yemeni homeland. 
  He delivered an important national speech which touched on 
developments on the national arena. He urged everyone to stick 
together in a single front to defend unity and Constitutional 
legitimacy and pool efforts to build the new Yemen under the 
banner of unity and democracy. 

</TEXT>

