Israel's arrogant policies, and its stands obstructing the 
achievement of a just and comprehensive peace in the region. 
  In this regard, the foreign minister urged the Russian 
Federation and the United States, in their capacity as the peace 
process sponsors, to denounce these Israeli policies and stands, 
particularly the recent terroristic kidnapping operation carried 
out by the Israeli troops inside the Lebanese territory. 
  The talks also dealt with relations between Syria and Russia 
and means of promoting them. 

