<H3> <TI>   Premier, Iranian Envoy Discuss Expansion of Ties </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Premier, Iranian Envoy Discuss Expansion of Ties </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2605082194 Tehran IRNA in English 0418 GMT 26 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2605082194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Damascus, May 26, IRNA -- Iran and Syria Wednesday 
[25 May] discussed ways to upgrade bilateral ties and reviewed 
matters of mutual interest. 
  The talks were held here between Iran's Ambassador to Syria 
Hojjat ol-Eslam Mohammad Hasan Akhtari and Syrian Prime Minister 
Mahmud al-Zu'bi. 
  During the meeting Hojjat ol-Eslam Akhtari submitted a 
message to the Syrian premier from Iranian First Vice-President 
Hasan Habibi for an official visit to Iran. 

</TEXT>

