  [Text] Lebanon has denied that it received any Israeli 
offer to withdraw from the south and western al-Biqa'. An 
authoritative Foreign Ministry source said: The Foreign 
Ministry would like to explain that this report is untrue. It 
hopes the media will be accurate with their reports, especially 
regarding issues relating to Lebanon's foreign policy and the 
negotiating process in the Middle East. 

