<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-NES-94-102 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  18 May 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> Pakistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Russian Deputy Foreign Minister Pays Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Deputy Foreign Minister Pays Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Spokesman Comments on Visit </H4>

<F P=102> BK1905003894 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network in Urdu 1500 
GMT 18 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1905003894 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network </F>
<F P=105>  Urdu </F>


