<F P=102>   LD2605084394 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian 0630 GMT 26 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2605084394 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network </F>

<F P=105>  Persian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Islamic President of Iran Mr. 
Hashemi-Rafsanjani arrived in Mashhad this morning. He was 
welcomed at the airport by Hojjat ol-Eslam val-Moslemin 
Va'ez-Tabasi, custodian of the Razavi holy shrine and the 
vali-ye faqih's representative in Khorasan; Mr. Mofidi, the 
governor-general; and local officials of the province. After 
arriving at Mashhad airport, Mr. Hashemi-Rafsanjani told a 
correspondent of the Central News Unit that the objective of 
this visit is to pay his respect to Imam Reza, peace be upon 
him, to open a consulate office of the Turkmenistan Republic in 
Mashhad, and to hold a series of economic talks with President 
Saparmurad Niyazov of Turkmenistan. 
  Simultaneous with arrival of the Islamic president of Iran 
in 
holy Mashhad, Mr. Saparmurad Niyazov also arrived at the head of 
a high-ranking delegation. He was welcomed at the airport by 
President Hashemi-Rafsanjani. 

