<H3> <TI>   `Fourth Phase' Recounted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Fourth Phase' Recounted </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2505125794 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network in 
Persian 1130 GMT 25 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2505125794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Persian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In continuation of the Ra'd-7 [Thunder-7] military 
exercise in the Darenjan region of Shiraz, the operations 
entered its fourth phase. During this exercise infantry units, 
an airborne division, and tank units crossed minefields and 
barbed wire with the support of the ground forces artillery and 
helicopters and the air force of the Islamic Republic of Iran. 
They captured various obstacles and dug canals. It is worth 
mentioning that after completion of this phase, the 
participating units were deployed in their defense positions. 

