<H3> <TI>   Khalifah, Delegation Return From Nairobi Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Khalifah, Delegation Return From Nairobi Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AB2205202694 Khartoum SUNA in French 1125 GMT 22 May 94 </F>
