<H4>    Aden Radio Reports 12 Injured in Attack </H4>

<F P=102> EA2605190794 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network 
in Arabic 1500 GMT 26 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA2605190794 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network 
