<H3> <TI>   Closure Lifted on Gaza Strip </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Closure Lifted on Gaza Strip </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA2705045594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 27 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2705045594 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The closure on the Gaza Strip was lifted this 
morning, and Palestinians are being allowed to enter Israel 
under the conditions enforced last week. The closure was 
imposed last Friday, following the terror attack near the Erez 
checkpoint in which reserves soldiers Moshe Bukra and Erez 
Ben-Barukh were killed. Since the attack the Palestinian police 
have set up roadblocks on the approach roads to entrance from 
the Strip and are stopping and examining local vehicles. 

</TEXT>

