<F P=102>   TA2505105994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1000 GMT 25 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2505105994 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] First to the dramatic disclosure that Israel 
and the Vatican are formulating an agreement in which the 
Catholic Church accepts indirect responsibility for 
anti-Semitism from ancient times up to the Holocaust. We have 
more details in this report from Dick Winter: 
  [Begin Winter recording] The historic agreement, which was 
drafted by an interreligious commission from Israel and the 
Vatican, states that a frightful mixture of racism, along with 
religious, political, social, and economic hostility against the 
Jewish people throughout history, created the basis for the 
Holocaust, and the Catholic Church did not do enough to oppose 
it. 
  One of the chief Israeli members of the commission, Rabbi 
David Rosen, says the draft is a major achievement and that the 
Vatican goes farther than even he ever expected it to go. 
[passage omitted] 
  Also in the document: the Vatican's acceptance of 
responsibility for creating in its teachings an atmosphere of 
hatred toward the Jewish people. Rabbi Rosen says he believes 
that the draft agreement will now be endorsed by the Pope. [end 
recording] 

</TEXT>

